{"tid":1528004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲覺得呢場仗有得贏嘅入一入嚟，等我屌醒你","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:03:02.000Z","uid":160887,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e0bfdfbbb76fb62619d4032a966cf64972c32b7b","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"經歷左咁多次遊行，示威，政府都冇作出回應<br />\n就知道無可能會滿足我哋嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n老老實實你比着我係林鄭，都諗唔到點樣拆而家香港嗰局<br />\n而家最後我哋唯一可以做嘅就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒</span></span>唔係單單出嚟遊行示威就係，而係做實質嘅行動去迫使國際出手又或者令到香港嘅金融系統崩壞，從而影響到大陸<br />\n<br />\n但大家仲好似未有呢個覺悟<br />\n地鐵閘仲未敢跳<br />\n美金拎左兩日就無哂聲氣<br />\n工都仲未敢罷？<br />\n<br />\n如果你仲係覺得而家呢份工係緊要過你以後嘅自由嘅話<br />\n咁你就唔值得擁有自由，民主<br />\n我建議你返返大陸安居樂業<br />\n<br />\n試問你對唔對得着俾人打到手腳斷嘅手足？<br />\n對唔對得着俾人強姦既女手足？<br />\n嗰幾位以死明志既義士？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家除咗上街之外可以組織更多嘅活動<br />\n去玩爛香港嘅金融政治<br />\n最基本繼續拎美金，罷買，塞機場<br />\n繼續做好文宣迫使國際出手<br />\n<br />\n離我哋攬炒嘅日子已經唔遠<br />\n共勉之<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831傷者情況未明</span></span>"},{"pid":"3452b6a024b39bf55c9608812f2cabd8c9e4549e","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a02158c39dce92a2bc7cca3ecbbd9341653b8f","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae206a4751d3f3f16757b3609bf1e3dd837ea7aa","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f57c7c373fb352af64df5503202b17a9e0e77ac","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859f7e62ff4c0270a81f946101f133db7a161b64","tid":1528004,"uid":259345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYsuvmW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYsuvmW.jpg&h=f8dbcaad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入黎幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n [推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b03226032b1d77f4dede5def4f9d8407916ec31a","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95966f629aeb009e85c5af8374feb688e39fb90","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00976cde719036469891fa53b88721bc12ba3a51","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1a39a1fc960a74fdb8140a28853260c0bfe9a5","tid":1528004,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"負評既人泥出下聲"},{"pid":"2ef6c4c627683700b5561efcc78971a2a2d02410","tid":1528004,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />